      "name": "Sons of Horus",
      "subtitle": "XVI Legion · The Luperci",
      "color": "#2D937D",
      "lore": "History records that it is the Sons of Horus Legion who lit the spark of rebellion and stood upon the ashes of the old Imperium. They above all others stand as a byword for treason to their foes, and as exemplars of resistance to adherents. They are the force of ambition, ruthlessness, and unbowed determination. Led by their charismatic Primarch Horus Lupercal, their every action is driven by a burning desire to carve out their own destiny in the stars.",
