        "name": "Death Dealers",
        "description": "When taking an Engage action, Infantry units add +1 to their Firefight value (up to a maximum of 2+)."
      },
      "compositionRules": [
        "Max 3 Support detachments per Line detachment in the army.",
        "Max 4 Upgrades per formation.",
        "Max 1/3 of total points value may be spent on Lords of War or Allies.",
        "Reaver, Luperci and Justaerian Detachments: 1 per 2,000 pts each.",
        "Primarch Horus may only be taken once and counts as your Supreme Commander."
